</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uqualtarshylok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qualtar Shylok</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Traveller of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 160<br> <font color=#CC9900>(1/13/01 8:11:53 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/blood_inferno/images/QualtarShylok.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: &lt;-- Ignorant Paranoia Sets In</span><hr size=1> Nah, you just have to get your skill (200) in board camping up! <br>
